quran[13{c,v,t}:
42,32,Wa min Aayaatihil ja waarifil bahri kal a'lam
42,33,Iny yashaaa yuskinir reeha fa yazlalna rawaakida 'alaa zahirh; inna fee zaalika la Aayaatil likulli sabbaarin shakoor
42,34,Aw yoobiqhunna bimaa kasaboo wa ya'fu 'an kaseer
42,35,Wa ya'lamal lazeena yujaadiloona feee Aayaatinaa maa lahum mim mahees
42,36,Famaa ooteetum min shai'in famataa'ul hayaatid dunyaa wa maa 'indal laahi khairunw wa abqaa lillazeena aamanoo wa 'alaa Rabbihim yatawakkaloon
42,37,Wallazeena yajtaniboona kabaaa'iral ismi wal fawaa hisha wa izaa maa ghadiboo hum yaghfiroon
42,38,Wallazeenas tajaaboo li Rabbhim wa aqaamus Salaata wa amruhum shooraa bainahum wa mimmaa razaqnaahum yunfiqoon
42,39,Wallazeena izaa asaabahumul baghyu hum yantasiroon
42,40,Wa jazaaa'u saiyi'atin saiyi'tum misluha faman 'afaa wa aslaha fa ajruhoo 'alal laah; innahoo laa yuhibbuz zaalimeen
42,41,Wa lamanin tasara ba'da zulmihee fa ulaaa'ika maa 'alaihim min sabeel
42,42,Innamas sabeelu 'alal lazeena yazlimoonan naasa wa yabghoona fil ardi bighairil haqq; ulaaa'ika lahum 'azaabun aleem
42,43,Wa laman sabara wa ghafara inna zaalika lamin 'azmil umoor�(section 4)
42,44,Wa mai yudlilil laahu famaa lahoo minw waliyyim mim ba'dih; wa taraz zaalimeena lammaa ra awul 'azaaba yaqooloona hal ilaa maraddim min sabeel
